{
  "id": "69f13c8bc9ec623d2d81c701",
  "title": "フロウ",
  "created": 1777417359,
  "updated": 1777437596,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f13c8bc9ec623d2d81c701",
      "text": "フロウ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417359,
      "updated": 1777417426
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13cd80000000000f33d21",
      "text": "ラップにおける[節回し]と訳される。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417433,
      "updated": 1777417465
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13cf50000000000f33d22",
      "text": "どこにアクセントを持ってくるか等がフロウの中心的な構成要素だろう。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417462,
      "updated": 1777417501
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1413f0000000000f33d32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418563,
      "updated": 1777418563
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1413f0000000000f33d33",
      "text": "ZORNとMACCOの曲",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418563,
      "updated": 1777418571
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1414b0000000000f33d34",
      "text": "[https://youtu.be/tjPQVvUHi3g?si=mLlw_5hrxKMX9M6t]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418572,
      "updated": 1777418573
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1414d0000000000f33d35",
      "text": " 2人のリズムやアクセントの使い方が全く異なる。もちろん全体的な雰囲気も違うのだが、特に発音の技法でもって個性が出るというのがフロウという言い方のコンセプトだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418573,
      "updated": 1777418858
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1423f0000000000f33d37",
      "text": " > ビートに韻とかフロウだけ乗せても退屈 ドラマが見えてこねえんだよ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418816,
      "updated": 1777418838
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b990000000000aef70e",
      "text": " 超かっこよ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777437594,
      "updated": 1777437596
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13d1d0000000000f33d23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417501,
      "updated": 1777417501
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13c8e0000000000f33d1d",
      "text": "[migos]の三連フロウ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417359,
      "updated": 1777417515
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13c9b0000000000f33d1f",
      "text": "[https://open.spotify.com/track/0M9ydKzuF3oZTfYYPfaGX1?si=w4WtCAlUTaKq8dVQMVnryQ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417372,
      "updated": 1777417677
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13e760000000000f33d25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417847,
      "updated": 1777417847
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13e770000000000f33d26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417847,
      "updated": 1777417847
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13ec20000000000f33d29",
      "text": "[HARKA]と[7]のフロウが似ていた螺旋",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417922,
      "updated": 1777418005
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13efc0000000000f33d2b",
      "text": " それぞれの1人め。これはわかりやすい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417980,
      "updated": 1777418010
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13fab0000000000f33d2d",
      "text": " 音程の取り方とかがなりを入れるタイミングとかもフロウの感じられ方に影響しているのだろう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418155,
      "updated": 1777418201
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13c9b0000000000f33d20",
      "text": "[https://youtu.be/3Fcp2K-pwhg?si=F5ODoAzOgPUe6p6X]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417372,
      "updated": 1777417919
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13ea50000000000f33d27",
      "text": "[https://youtu.be/ajSQb6NYl1Q?si=57ZRXsUJcoC5NckX]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417916,
      "updated": 1777417919
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13ebe0000000000f33d28",
      "text": "この2人は和歌山勢である",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777417919,
      "updated": 1777418221
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13fed0000000000f33d2e",
      "text": "同じく和歌山の[MIKADO]はHARKAとともに[WAKA FLOW]という曲を出している。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418221,
      "updated": 1777418404
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1405c0000000000f33d31",
      "text": "7はHARKAに合わせたところもあるかもしれないけど、これが和歌山っぽいフロウというのが螺旋当時も今も確立されてるわけでないので似ているのは微妙になってしまったと思う",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777418332,
      "updated": 1777418432
    },
    {
      "id": "69f13ffe0000000000f33d2f",
